      <title>富时 100 指数因盈利乐观而延续创纪录涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/ftse-100-extends-record-run-earnings-optimism-2024-04-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国富时 100 指数周三延续创纪录的涨幅，利洁时 (Reckitt Benckiser) 强劲的盈利报告和大宗商品股的上涨抵消了劳埃德银行集团 (Lloyds Banking Group) 在报告季度利润下滑后表现不佳的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/ftse-100-extends-record-run-earnings-optimism-2024-04-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 07:35:07 GMT</pubDate>
