      <title>英国劳埃德银行预计第一季度利润因收入紧缩而下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/britains-lloyds-bank-says-q1-profit-falls-28-2024-04-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[劳埃德银行集团第一季度税前利润下滑 28%，原因是成本上升、利率见顶以及抵押贷款市场竞争加剧损害了收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/britains-lloyds-bank-says-q1-profit-falls-28-2024-04-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 06:09:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
